description: The UBS AG FI Enhanced Europe 50 ETN are a series of FI Enhanced ETNs linked to the STOXX Europe 50 USD (Gross Return) Index. The Securities are senior unsecured debt securities issued by UBS AG (UBS). The index is derived from the STOXX Europe 600 Index (the “parent index”), which is further subdivided into 19 STOXX Regional Total Market Index (TMI) Supersector Indices (the “Supersector Indices”). The index is composed of 50 European blue-chip companies from within the parent index.
name: UBS AG FI Enhanced Europe 50 ETN
